    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, but it's a bit too generic for our high-net-worth clients. They value the personal touch and the specific way you handle their complex itineraries. Can you add a section that compares the current service style with what they should expect from the new, faster engine? They'll want to know if they'll lose any of that personalized concierge feel they've grown used to.",
