      "content": "For your VIP clients, we need to emphasize continuity despite the upgrade. You can assure them that while the engine is being optimized for speed, the core essence of our personalized concierge service remains untouched. The new system is engineered to *enhance* our ability to manage their complex itineraries, providing faster access to real-time data while maintaining the bespoke attention they expect from us. This upgrade means quicker responses to their intricate travel needs, not less personal care.",
